  <p>These are the rules and guidelines for the ♪ EDM Spot ♪ Plug.dj room.</p>
  <p>Rules may be changed at any time. Ignorance doesn&#39;t protect from enforcement of the rules.</p>

  <br>

  <h3 class="fr-text-bordered"><strong>Song Rules:</strong></h3>
  <p>A song must follow all rules to be acceptable. That means AMVs have to be in-genre! With exception for very Chill
    songs.</p>
  <br>
  <p>● Genres: <strong>EDM</strong> and <strong>Chill</strong></p>
  <p>● Bass-Boosted and Nightcore songs will be skipped - Please use a normal version of the song.</p>
  <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ Songs with bass added are not an issue. Songs that require the volume to be adjusted
    to hear the song normally, are.</p>

  <p>● Acceptable Languages: English or Japanese</p>

  <p style="margin-left: 20px;">&nbsp;○ Foreign songs, not in English or Japanese, may result in an immediate ban with
    no warning.(samples and snippets of other languages are fine, if you have a song in question, please ask staff
    before playing)</p>

  <p>● AMVs (Anime Music Videos) are allowed.</p>

  <p>● Ear rape/jumpscare songs are not allowed and will result in a permanent ban.</p>

  <p>● NSFW songs are not allowed. This applies to the video and the lyrics of the song, and includes racism, hate
    speech, acts of violence or overtly graphic sexual content.</p>

  <p>● Politics and Religion: Songs mustn&#39;t address politics or religion.</p>

  <p>● Song history: Songs mustn&#39;t play again within 6 hours. This applies to different remixes as well.</p>

  <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ Songs Played 8 Times in 2 weeks will be considered Overplayed and will be skipped for 5 Days</p>

  <p>● Song length mustn&#39;t be longer than 6 minutes and 30 seconds.</p>

  <p>● Intros and outros within videos are fine if they:</p>

  <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ Have music that complies with the other rules</p>

  <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ No advertising of any kind (this includes personal channels, and other plug.dj rooms)</p>

  <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ Aren&#39;t longer than 10-15 seconds</p>

  <p>● Songs have to be of a certain audio quality. Videos of live performances with bad quality are not allowed.</p>

  <p>● Troll songs are NOT allowed.</p>

  <p>
    <br>
  </p>

  <p><strong>Song skipping</strong></p>

  <p>● Songs that don&#39;t comply with the song rules will be skipped.</p>

  <p>● You will not get your spot back if your song is skipped unless is skipped for history or overplayed and you are not AFK.</p>

  <p>● Individual punishments for not following the rules may be issued.</p>

  <p>● Don&#39;t ask for skips in chat.</p>

  <p>● Songs that reach a certain &quot;Meh&quot; threshold of 6% of online community will be skipped. Hardcore and
    Hardstyle songs will be subject to a 4% threshold, so that we can avoid the harder or classic styles of these
    subgenres.</p>
