  <p><strong>Producers and Promoters</strong></p>

  <p>● Only Producers Verified by Staff are allowed to play their own music. (This includes if the person playing the song had any part of
    the creation of the song)</p>

    <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ Producers should play other songs than theirs if they can't comply with this DO NOT Rule:</p>
    <p style="margin-left: 40px;">○ Playing same small playlist over and over. (to avoid same songs being played all the time)</p>
    <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ Give and Take is important. Producers should be able to promote our room.</p>
    <p style="margin-left: 40px;">○ We'll check this from time to time. If you haven't done this recently at the check time the verified status will be removed.</p>
    <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ If you play a song that doesn't follow the rules you will lose the verified status.</p>
    <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ If you are a producer you can apply here: http://tinyurl.com/edmspotproducersprogram</p>

  <p>● Promoters that uploaded music produced by other artists (not yourself) are allowed to play from your channel,
    however:</p>

  <p style="margin-left: 20px;">&nbsp;○ Promoted music below a certain quality threshold will be skipped.</p>

  <p style="margin-left: 20px;">○ Advertising your channel or account is not allowed. Doing so will result in a warning
    and in a ban on further violations.</p>
