  <h3 class="fr-text-bordered"><strong>Community Guidelines:</strong></h3>

  <p>These guidelines apply to the chat and usernames within the EDMSpot Plug.DJ room.</p>

  <p>● We&#39;re here to have fun within the community and listen to music together.</p>

  <p>● We&#39;re not here to argue over rules or to find loopholes in them.</p>

  <p>● Where rules do not prevail, common sense shall.</p>

  <p>
