  <p><strong>SFW Policy:&nbsp;</strong></p>

  <p>We want to keep our community SFW (Safe For Work). So songs, their thumbnails, chat messages, and user profiles
    deemed NSFW (Not Safe For Work) are not allowed!&nbsp;</p>

  <p>
    <br>
  </p>

  <p><strong>NSFW:</strong></p>

  <p>Content that includes anyone or anything actively involved in a sexual manner in a video.&nbsp;</p>

  <p>For example, men/women indecently exposed with garments less than normal outside bikinis or swimming accessories,
    sexual harassment, hate speech (racial slurs, sexual slurs) or overtly violent and offensive videos showcasing
    someone or thing getting hurt or killed.</p>

  <p>
    <br>
  </p>

  <p>Banned NSFW channels: HentaiDude</p>

  <p>Breaking the SFW policy will likely result in a permanent ban from the community.</p>

  <p>
    <br>
  </p>

  <p><strong>Asking for skips:</strong></p>

  <p>We use &quot;Meh&#39;s&quot; to skip songs, so please don&#39;t ask for skips or a Meh in chat since it
    doesn&#39;t add any value to chat.</p>

  <p>Doing so will result in a warning, mute, or ban.</p>

  <p>
    <br>
  </p>

  <p><strong>Bad-mouthing songs:</strong></p>

  <p>Please understand that we respect your opinion, but voicing a negative opinion about a song does not add anything
    of value to the chat. Please just Meh and mute the song if you do not like it. Doing otherwise will be considered
    spam in the chat and be treated as having asked for a skip.</p>

  <p>
    <br>
  </p>

  <p><strong>Arguing with staff:</strong></p>

  <p>We understand that you may not agree with the &ldquo;what or how&rdquo;, but the staff are doing their job. While
    having a discussion is one thing, Arguing with the staff in chat or trash talking them will do no good. Please PM
    the staff member you have a disagreement with, and try to resolve the problem. If you have an issue with a staff
    member, please DM **Laquett** ( Laquett#1006 ) on discord. If you disrespect the staff, ignore warnings or request
    from staff, or are trying to disrupt the actions of the staff you will face punishment, regardless of your rank.</p>
